page_0: ".
   Agloras Coranth!
   Kaglimorex thelorun asu
   enlien Balmrorven agror.
   Kalu Fendith? Kalu Kalid?
   Akilno! Akilno Cleas!
   Po walnarus veor.

   Sigliop ulanis friopic,
   ru phulin Gorax!

   Hakannen bxs'hanthu
   jiollux plenfanth, er
   hujeris feroth.

   Phir tun Ferunith!"




 